  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main purpose of the study is to examine to which extent abnormalities in the dynamics of
      neural activities observed in patients with psychosis is related to difficulties at ordering
      simple visual stimuli and/or personal events.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
